node.text:
PepsiCo is partnering with Boston Beer to launch new Hard Mtn Dew in early 2022. They expect to launch three flavors: Original, Black Cherry, and Watermelon. Each drink is 5% ABV. The press release does not mention the caffeine content od the drinks. 

News and images via The Boston Beer Company.

What are your thoughts on this release?

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by CandyHunting on August 10, 2021 tagging @kelloggsus, and @cheezit. May be an image of food.

node.text:
Cheez-It is launching a new online store and three exclusive, online-only flavors! The website, shop.cheezit.com, already has lots of Cheez-It merchandise for sale. 

The new flavors are part of an Extra Toasty Superfan 4-Pack. In addition to Extra Toasty, the pack also includes Extra Toasty Extra Spicy, Extra Toasty Extra Cheesy, and Extra Toasty Cheddar Jack. The pack is available for $19.99 starting tomorrow, August 11, at 12pm Eastern. 

News and images via Kellogg's.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by CandyHunting on August 10, 2021 tagging @krispykreme, @hersheycompany, and @hersheys. May be an image of dessert and text.

node.text:
Happy National S'mores Day!

Krispy Kreme has new Hershey's S'mores donuts out starting today for a limited time in the US and Canada! 

There are two varieties:

S’mores Classic Doughnut: A doughnut filled with marshmallow kreme, dipped in Hershey’s chocolate icing, drizzled with marshmallow kreme and chocolate icing and topped with graham cracker crumbs.

S’mores Fudge Cake Doughnut: A Hershey’s fudge cake doughnut, dipped in marshmallow icing, decorated with Hershey’s chocolate icing and topped with chocolate chips. 

News and images via Krispy Kreme.

node.text: Well, I never would have expected to see a Field of Dreams cereal. Hy-Vee has this cereal out ahead of the August 12th game between the Chicago White Sox and New York Yankees in Dyersville, Iowa. Part of the proceeds go toward the Comfort Zone Camp, a nonprofit that helps children who have lost an immediate family member.

node.text:
New Skittles Shriekers are out now for Halloween! These are available in bags of fun size packs, share size, and single size. I found them at Blain's Farm & Fleet, while others have spotted the single size at CVS.

The Shriekers mix contains Shocking Lime, Spine-Tingling Tangerine, Citrus Scream, Rattled Raspberry, and Ghoulish Green Apple flavors. Additionally, some of the Skittles are very sour and hidden in the mix by sharing the same colors as the flavors listed.

node.text:
Reese's Footballs are back! I found these as 10 packs at Walmart near the registers. Others have spotted them as single and double packs. 

Reese's Footballs were also out in 2016 as these shape, minis, and a giant 8 oz size. They were also out in 2010 as minis.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by CandyHunting on August 06, 2021 tagging @hyvee, @snickers, and @marswrigley. May be an image of food.

node.text:
Here are the new Snickers Almond Brownie & Dark Chocolate Squares! I found the stand up bags at Hy-Vee, and others have found the bars at stores including Walmart and Walgreens. 

This is the second Snickers Brownie candy bar, after the Peanut variety debuted last December. While the Peanut Brownie has a strong peanut flavor, the Almond Brownie has little almond flavor. There is some crunch from the almonds, but the flavor is dominated by the dark chocolate, chewy brownie filling, and caramel. I'm not a huge fan of almonds, so no almond flavor is a win for me. 

The Snickers Almond Brownie bars are pretty darn good! I would rank these slightly above the Peanut variety, but that is purely personal preference.
